<span id="freeTextContainer18349120355178158634"><strong>Intense</strong><br/><br/>I liked the storyline and characters but I feel like there should have been a little more building of the relationships between the main and secondary characters, to give us readers a better connection with Corey. But in all it was a great story!</span>

